	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is your question on how to add a copier header or change the filename? I get confused because emulators will recognize a copier extension like SMC, but don't care if it's in the proper ROM+(SMC)Header format for which the extension was created to denote. You can add an empty header with NSRT.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


